		IF LOCAL:24 > 0
			IF DICE_SUM == 3
				GET_MONEY += 15 * LOCAL:24
				IF LANGUAGE == "ENG"
					PRINTW Those who have bet on "3" will receive 15 times dividend.
				ELSE
					PRINTW 「『３』に賭けていた方には15倍の配当が入ります。」
